<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-14a2861f-a3a1-402c-ba93-ad1bae5fb148'>
            
<p class="">35.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
                Mr. David Adams 
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-18/debates/3686c9aa-0394-4674-ac92-1c46ce066f84/SnowstormDamageTyneside#contribution-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Labour whether he is aware that, resulting from the recent severe snowstorm upon Tyneside, large quantities of cast iron and wooden spouts and gutters have been destroyed, and in the absence of which rapid deterioration of property and serious danger to health has ensued; and whether he will obtain the release of the requisite skilled labour from the Services in order to effect the repairs?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-18/debates/3686c9aa-0394-4674-ac92-1c46ce066f84/SnowstormDamageTyneside#contribution-f98dc375-1bdc-40d5-a280-493f253aedcf">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
                The Joint Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministry of Labour (Mr. Tomlinson)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-18/debates/3686c9aa-0394-4674-ac92-1c46ce066f84/SnowstormDamageTyneside#contribution-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My right hon. Friend is having inquiries made and will write to the hon. Member, but I have no evidence at present that damage of this character is so serious and extensive as to justify an application for release of men from the Army to effect repairs.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-18/debates/3686c9aa-0394-4674-ac92-1c46ce066f84/SnowstormDamageTyneside#contribution-af13ec16-1956-46ae-bbdc-4a7c4e06ef37">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c68d955e-312c-440a-be32-b32739f68846">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-c68d955e-312c-440a-be32-b32739f68846">
